{
  "texts": [
    "ChatGPT based on GPT-4 scored 65% when answering Japanese questions from the Japan Radiology Board Examination (JRBE) [44].",
    "Another study evaluated ChatGPT's performance on the Polish specialty exam in radiology and diagnostic imaging.",
    "Although ChatGPT did not reach the passing threshold of 52%, it came close in certain question categories [45].",
    "Although the precise performance of LLMs may exhibit variance based on language [46], these facts suggest that LLMs may be able to play a supplementary role even in quite specialized radiology work, even if only for text data at this point.Given the demonstrated capabilities of LLMs, there exists a potential to significantly enhance radiological workflow.",
    "This enhancement may manifest through proficient summarization of medical records, streamlined diagnostic imaging studies, clinical decision-making, rewriting, and generation of radiology reports [47,48]."
  ]
}